    id: "tpl-0030-i-have-a-system-error-after-downloading-and-laun",
    name: "I have a System error after downloading and launching the new client (MACos)?",
    tags: ["uncategorized"],
    opening: "Hello,",
    body: "Thank you for your email.\n\nIf you’re using the Mac desktop client and see an error saying the app was blocked, please follow these steps:\n\n- Open System Settings.\n- Go to Privacy & Security.\n- Scroll down until you see the message:\n“CoinPoker was blocked because it is not from an identified developer.”\n- Click Open Anyway.\n- Confirm once more when prompted.\n\nThis will allow the application to run normally.\nPlease reach out if you have any further questions or if the issue remains unresolved.",
