    body: "Thank you for your email.\nA fully updated MTT schedule — covering both regular tournaments and Satellites — has been launched on the new platform, offering a wider selection of poker formats and buy‑ins to suit every type of player.\nThe schedule will continue to grow and expand over the coming weeks and months, with new events added regularly.  Please keep an eye on the client and our website for upcoming updates and further details.\nIf you have any further questions, please feel free to let us know.",
