    body: "Thanks for your email.\n\nPlease first make sure you removed the old client from your device and have installed the new version as per the download links available here: https://download.coinpoker.com/en/download\n\nThen re-attempt login ensuring you have entered the correct email address and password. \n\nIf the above steps yet fail, please reset your password by clicking on \"Reset password\". If issues persists please provide a screenshot of the error you are receiving and specify what is your device and operative system.\n\nWe remain available to assist you further.",
