    body: "Thank you for contacting CoinPoker.\nI can confirm that our software is completely safe. Occasionally, antivirus programs flag applications downloaded from the internet simply because they come from an unfamiliar source, not because they contain a threat.\nPlease also check your VPN or firewall settings, as these can sometimes block access to the application. Temporarily disabling your firewall or antivirus during the download may help resolve the issue, after which you can re‑enable them as normal. Additionally, please be advised that we do not endorse the use of VPNs.\nIf you need any further assistance, feel free to reach out to us again.",
