    name: "Withdrawal Info",
    tags: ["needs editing: https://cpgroupglobal.slack.com/archives/c0708labg4q/p1772633086331419"],
    opening: "Hello,",
    body: "Thank you for your email.\n\nPlease be aware that you can only withdraw from the “Withdrawable” balance shown in your wallet.\n\nTo make a withdrawal, go to your “Wallet”, choose the cryptocurrency you want your USDT withdrawal to be sent to, and enter the address of a private wallet you own that supports that currency.  Processing times will vary depending on network activity.\n\nYou can withdraw as follows:\n\n- USDT on the Ethereum, Binance Smart Chain,  Polygon, Solana and Tron networks\n- USDC on the Ethereum or Polygon network.\n- BTC on the Bitcoin network (available only if you deposited BTC previously)\n\nPlease note that withdrawal fees apply and will depend on the currency and network you choose.\n\nIf you have any further questions, please let us know.",
