    id: "tpl-0045-change-your-username",
    name: "Change Your Username?",
    tags: ["uncategorized"],
    opening: "Hello,",
    body: "Thank you for your email.\n\nJust a quick note to explain how the “Change Your Username” option works on CoinPoker:\n\n- When you first sign up, you won’t see the Change Username pop‑up during your initial session.\n- You can change your username at any time using the widget on the mobile or desktop homepage.\n- If you haven’t changed it—or tapped Keep the Same—by your third session, a pop‑up will appear asking you to choose. This is the final time the option will be shown. If you do not change after the final time, you will no longer be able to change your nickname.\n\nA new session is counted when one of the following happens:\n\n- You’ve been away from the app for 30 minutes or more, or\n- You log out and log back in.\n\nIf you have any further questions, just let us know—we’re here to help.",
