    id: "tpl-0048-rakeback-earned-how-to-find",
    name: "Rakeback earned - How to find?",
    tags: ["uncategorized"],
    opening: "Hello,",
    body: "Thank you for your email.\nRakeback is credited daily at 8:00 UTC. You can view it under My Profile → Transactions → Rewards. All rakeback payments are added to your Rewards balance in your Wallet, and you can transfer them to your Withdrawal balance by clicking “Transfer Now.”  \nMore details: https://coinpoker.com/promotions/rakeback/\nDuring the 100% Rakeback promotion, CoinRace winnings are deducted from your daily rakeback and paid out at the end of each 2‑hour leaderboard. You still receive the full 100% through to March 31.\n• Example: If you earn $100 in rakeback and win $40 in CoinRaces, your payout the next morning (by 8:00 UTC) will be $60.\nPlease note that game fees vary between Cash Games, All‑In or Fold, Tournaments, and VIP (High‑Stakes) Games.\nIf you have any further questions, feel free to reach out. Best of luck at the tables.",
