    body: "Thank you for contacting us.\n\nTo help us review your case, please first provide the Ticket ID or a screenshot showing the full bet details.\n\nYou can find the Ticket ID by opening Sportsbook → My Bets → All and selecting the relevant bet. The Ticket ID appears at the bottom of the entry—simply tap Copy Ticket ID and include it in your reply.\nNote, if there is no Ticket ID is displayed; please instead provide the VD… number, which can be found under Wallet → My Transactions → Sportsbook.\n\nIf you’re referring to a Casino bet, please open My Transactions → Casino and provide the VD number shown there\n\nOnce we have this information, we’ll be able to assist you further.",
