    body: "Thank you for your email.\n\nWe apologise for the inconvenience caused. There was an issue that affected some players when claiming the Casino bonus. In certain cases, even after making an eligible deposit and selecting the bonus, it was not awarded correctly.\n\nPlease note that Casino bonuses cannot be applied retroactively, so you will need to make another eligible deposit in order to claim it.\n\nYou can view your Casino Bonus details and track your progress by going to: My Profile > Wallet > Casino Bonuses.\n\nThank you for your understanding, and best of luck at the tables.",
