    id: "tpl-0063-poker-reveal-hole-cards-to-opponents-after-the-a",
    name: "Poker - Reveal Hole Cards to opponents (after the active hand)",
    tags: ["poker"],
    opening: "Hello,",
    body: "Thank you for contacting us.\n\nTo reveal your hole cards, simply click on the card or cards you would like to show once the other players fold.\n\nWhen you select a card, a small eye icon will appear on it, indicating that the card will be revealed at the end of the hand. If you change your mind, you can click the card again to remove the selection before the hand finishes.\n\nPlease note that the selected cards will only be shown once all other players have folded and the hand is complete.\n\nIf you have any other questions, feel free to let us know and we’ll be happy to help.",
