    name: "Locate Missing Deposit (Successful deposit found)",
    tags: ["deposits"],
    opening: "Hello,",
    body: "Thank you for your email.\n\nYour credit was successful. To review your transactions, open My Profile and go to Transactions. Select Deposits (credits) or Withdrawals (debits), and make sure your filters on the left are enabled so all activity is visible.\n\nIf the transaction you’re looking for still doesn’t appear, please confirm whether it was a Bank Card or Crypto deposit/withdrawal and provide the full details.\n\nInclude the transaction ID (for bank/card payments) or the transaction hash (for crypto), along with a screenshot taken directly from the platform, wallet, or exchange where the transaction was initiated. The screenshot must clearly show the date and time, amount, and the ID/Hash, and feel free to cover personal information for your protection.\n\nIf you need anything else, just let us know.",
