    opening: "Hello,",
    body: "Thank you for your email.\nI understand the frustration with the delay in your funds being credited due to the system‑side issue, and we sincerely apologise for the inconvenience.\nPlease allow the full 5 business days to elapse for the credit to process. You can check the status under My Profile → Transactions → All, using the All Time filter.\nIf the funds are still not returned after the full 5‑business‑day period, please contact us with the ticket ID from your Sportsbook tab, or the VD number from your Transactions section so we can investigate further.\nThank you for your patience while this is resolved.",
