    body: "Thank you for reaching out.\n\nAt the moment, the option to set deposit limits is not available on the current version of our platform. We understand that the Help Desk section mentions this feature, and we apologize for any confusion this may have caused.\n\nPlease rest assured that our team is actively working on major platform improvements, and responsible gaming tools such as deposit limits are included in the enhancements currently being developed. We hope to introduce this functionality in a future update.\n\nIn the meantime, we can offer to temporarily close your account for a specific period or remove access to the Poker, Casino, or Sportsbook sections for either a set or indefinite amount of time. If you would like to proceed, please let us know which option you prefer and for how long you would like the restriction applied.\n\nWe truly appreciate your patience and understanding. If you have any other questions or need assistance, please feel free to contact us.",
