    id: "tpl-0088-rakeback-stage-2-16th-to-31st-march",
    name: "Rakeback  - Stage 2 (16th to 31st March)",
    tags: ["agreed with jw"],
    opening: "Hello,",
    body: "Thank you for your email.\n\nPlease find the simplified details for Stage 2 (March 16–31) — 100% rakeback every day across all formats:\n\n•        All Cash Games: 100% rakeback through a combination of flat rakeback and CoinRaces leaderboards paying $1,000,000 weekly.  Example: If you earn 15% from leaderboards, the remaining 85% is paid as flat rakeback.\n•        VIP Games: Always 100% flat rakeback.\n•        Tournaments: 100% rakeback on all buy-ins.\n\nDuring the 100% Rakeback promotion, CoinRace winnings are offset against your daily rakeback, but everyone still receives the full 100% through March 31.\n•        If you earn $100 in rakeback for the day and win $50 in CoinRaces, your rakeback payout the next morning, by 8am UTC will be $50.\nAll rakeback payments are credited to your Rewards balance in My Profile.\n\nRakeback details:  https://coinpoker.com/promotions/rakeback/\n\nBest of luck at the tables!",
    created_at: "2026-03-12T00:00:00Z",
