    tags: ["uncategorized"],
    opening: "Hello,",
    body: "Thank you for contacting CoinPoker Support.\nFor any affiliate related questions, it’s best to contact them directly at affiliates@coinpoker.com, as they exclusively manage all affiliate matters. This includes information such as affiliate codes, names, and account assignments, which our Support team cannot access.\nThe Affiliates team will review your case and get back to you within a few business days. They will address your concerns and provide any assistance needed.\nIf you have any other questions or need additional support in the meantime, feel free to contact us — we’re here to help.",
