    id: "tpl-0091-tech-high-cpu-performance-settings",
    name: "Tech - High CPU (performance settings)",
    tags: ["uncategorized"],
    opening: "Hello,",
    body: "Thank you for contacting us.\n\nThe new client may feel heavier than the previous version due to the improved graphics and visual elements. To improve performance, you can reduce the graphical load by enabling Reduce Animations in the client:\n\nTable Settings → Game Settings → Reduce Animations\n\nThis setting can help the tables run more smoothly, especially when multi-tabling or playing on older systems.\n\nLet us know if you have any further questions.",
