    opening: "Hello,",
    body: "We have received your messages.\n\nPlease be advised that we will not engage with or respond to communications containing abusive or offensive language. We are here to assist, but all interactions must remain respectful.\n\nDue to the nature of your recent communications, your account has been temporarily closed. To proceed with a potential reinstatement, you will need to confirm your acceptance of our Terms and Conditions and ensure that all future communication remains respectful.\n\nPlease note that any further abusive behaviour will not be tolerated and may result in the permanent closure of your account.\n\nIf you wish to continue, we invite you to resend your request in a civil manner.\n\nThank you for your understanding.\n\nCoinPoker Management",
