    id: "tpl-0110-mario-promo-s-giveaways-triton-giveaway",
    name: "Mario Promo's & Giveaways (Triton giveaway)",
    tags: ["uncategorized"],
    opening: "Hello,",
    body: "Thank you for your email.\n\nPlease make sure to review the full terms and conditions on how to qualify, available on the official giveaway page. Kindly ensure that you have completed all the necessary and required criteria within Mario’s promotion:\nhttps://mariomosboeck.at/tritongiveaway\n\nAs long as the conditions for the giveaway are met, you will be automatically registered into the next event. You may not see that you are registered right after meeting the conditions, but rest assured that all eligible players will be registered before start.\n\nIf you used — or believe you may have used — an incorrect code during entry, we will need to review this manually, as only correct affiliate codes count toward valid entries. Any entry submitted with an incorrect code cannot be counted automatically.\n\nIf you have any questions or need further assistance, feel free to let us know.",
