    body: "Thanks for your patience while we were sorting out your poker welcome bonus, which you had pending for release on our old client application.\n\nA locked bonus is now available in your cashier and funds are unlocked as you play. Here's how the 150% Welcome Bonus (up to $2,000) works:\n \n- Bonus funds are unlocked as you play. For every $1 generated in rake, $0.33 of bonus funds are moved directly to your Rewards Balance.\n- Both cash game and tournament rake count towards unlocking your bonus.\n- For cash games, the bonus is processed immediately after you leave the table — no need to wait for milestones.\n- For tournaments, the bonus is released at the end of the tournament, based on the cumulative rake you generated during play.\n- Every session you play unlocks more of your bonus.\n \nFor full details, you can visit: https://coinpoker.com/promotions/welcome-bonus/\n \nIf you have any further questions, please don't hesitate to reach out.",
