    name: "Tech - Auto-generated email not received",
    tags: ["uncategorized"],
    opening: "Hello,",
    body: "Thank you for contacting us.\n\nPlease make sure you only request one code, as asking for multiple ones won't work. If you're not receiving our email and already made sure to check the Spam folder, please whitelist and add our email address to your contacts. Here is a step-by-step guide:\n\n1. Open your email inbox\n2. Click Contacts (or Google Contacts if you use Gmail)\n3. Select Create new contact\n4. Add the email address: noreply@coinpoker.com\n5. Save the contact\n\nOnce you've done this, please also make sure our emails won't end up in your Spam folder:\n\n1. Open Gmail and click the settings icon\n2. Select See all settings\n3. Go to Filters and Blocked Addresses\n4. Click Create a new filter\n5. In the “From” field, enter: @coinpoker.com\n6. Click Create filter\n7. Check Never send it to Spam\n8. Save the filter\n\nIf you still don’t receive the email after this, please let us know, and we’ll assist further.",
